                "description": "A private key in PEM format for connecting to the server by using HTTPS. The private key must not be encrypted; it cannot be protected by a password or passphrase. If you specify a custom private key, you must also specify values for <code>CustomDomain</code> and <code>CustomCertificate</code>."
